{"tid":1981993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"肥過籠！傳金正恩接受心血管手術病危 美韓密切監察情報","createTime":"2020-04-21T03:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T04:38:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"06a3187a43e3d31b0f7f4c396d6af1cf44d31516","tid":1981993,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hiK38Sjd8ZBs2OdIOqSjqA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/aaf07bf0-8379-11ea-9fe7-9a50533fde7d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhiK38Sjd8ZBs2OdIOqSjqA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2Faaf07bf0-8379-11ea-9fe7-9a50533fde7d&h=7121d9bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北韓領導人金正恩上周三（15日）疑似缺席其祖父、已故領袖金日成的誕辰參謁活動，引起外界關注其健康狀況。專門報道北韓新聞的南韓傳媒周二（21日）報道，金正恩在月初曾接受心血管手術。美媒則報道，華府正密切監察有關金正恩已病危的情報。南韓多名官員表示並未掌握有關狀況，而統一部則表示無可奉告。<br />\n<br />\n主要由脫北者營運的韓媒「Daily NK」引述北韓匿名消息報道，金正恩在上周日（12日）於香山郡金剛山一間醫院接受了心血管手術，目前正在金剛山度假區休養治療。金正恩最後一次公開露面是在本月11日主持勞動黨中央政治局會議，據報他隨後即動身前往醫院。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，金正恩自去年8月已出現心血管毛病，但在近月數度登上白頭山後情況惡化。報道又指，金正恩是因為吸煙、肥胖及過勞等問題，導致其健康狀況在近月每況愈下。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線電視新聞網絡（CNN）則引述美國知情官員消息指，華府正留意金正恩在手術後情況嚴重的情報。韓聯社則報道，南韓政府一名負責對朝工作的負責人表示，尚未有線索可推測金正恩健康出現問題。該名消息人士指，金正恩不久前才現身公開活動，對有關報道是否可信提出質疑。<br />\n<br />\n北韓上周二（14日）曾向朝鮮半島東面海域發射多枚反艦短程巡航導彈，金正恩通常會現身監督同類試射，惟官媒朝中社事後未有發布金正恩到場的消息。朝中社亦未有報道金正恩在金日成108歲誕辰參謁太陽宮的消息，其時外媒估計金正恩或是因應新冠肺炎疫情而缺席。"},{"pid":"5264b57ca0b62a69fe9db79d4875b95092d05622","tid":1981993,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學毛新宇姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097413072573aa3a386b36668fdaca4cc797c226","tid":1981993,"uid":181822,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcw8Fpd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcw8Fpd.jpg&h=ca6c776a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢真係好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75d8f9fd9935b539d533865535780a73b1cd35d","tid":1981993,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"af392da69546f8392ee92ee629f8e36db92d6c16","tid":1981993,"uid":343376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"097413072573aa3a386b36668fdaca4cc797c226","tid":1981993,"uid":181822,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcw8Fpd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcw8Fpd.jpg&h=ca6c776a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢真係好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:45:32.000Z","msg":"金oppa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc44ed984185d6dd326edea8d474e81bb1960a46","tid":1981993,"uid":313054,"like":0,"dislike"